latestIgtvVideos.caption:
You can now create any theme decor at your home within minutes with our DIY quarantine decor packages. 
Check out how @karishmasamat used her creativity to decorate the room for her toddler's 7 months. 🎉🎈🧸
.
Quoting her"it took me about 10 mins to complete the whole set up.. 😁 I was super excited as this was the first time I’ve done something like this on my own without any professional help.. To be honest.. it was quite simple and looked sooooo cute 🤩 
Thankyou @balloon.blushh for organizing all the props and balloons 🎈🎈🎈"
